  "contenu": [
    {
      "type": "texte",
      "value": "<p>Une urne contient neuf boules identiques dont cinq sont de couleur blanche, trois de couleur rouge et une de couleur noire. On tire successivement et sans remise trois boules de cette urne, ce qui équivaut à tirer les trois boules simultanément. On considère deux variables aléatoires <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y\\)</span>, où <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\)</span> représente le nombre de boules blanches obtenues et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y\\)</span> le nombre de boules noires.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Déterminer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X(\\Omega)\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y(\\Omega)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(X(\\Omega)=\\{0,1,2,3\\}\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y(\\Omega)=\\{0,1\\}\\)</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Déterminer la loi de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\)</span> et calculer son espérance.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\sim \\mathcal{H}(3,\\frac{5}{9},9)\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\E(X)=3\\times \\frac{5}{9}=\\frac{5}{3}\\)</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Déterminer la loi de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y\\)</span> et calculer son espérance.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y\\sim \\mathcal{H}(3,\\frac{1}{9},9)\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\E(Y)=3\\times \\frac{1}{9}=\\frac{1}{3}\\)</span></p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Compléter le tableau de la loi conjointe du couple <span class=\"math inline\">\\((X,Y)\\)</span> :</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<table>\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"header\">\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y \\backslash X\\)</span></th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\">0</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\">1</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\">2</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\">3</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\p_Y\\)</span> (loi de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y\\)</span>)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{1}{84}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{15}{84}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{30}{84}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{10}{84}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{56}{84}\\)</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"even\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{3}{84}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{15}{84}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{10}{84}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(0\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{28}{84}\\)</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\p_X\\)</span> (loi de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\)</span>)</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{4}{84}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{30}{84}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{40}{84}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{10}{84}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(1\\)</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Les variables <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y\\)</span> sont-elles indépendantes ? Justifier.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>Les variables <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Y\\)</span> ne sont pas indépendantes. En effet,</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prob(X=3)=\\frac{10}{84}\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prob(Y=1)=\\frac{28}{84}\\)</span></p></li>\n<li><p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prob(X=3,Y=1)=0\\)</span></p></li>\n</ul>\n<p>donc <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prob(X=3,Y=1)\\neq \\prob(X=3)\\prob(Y=1)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>On pose <span class=\"math inline\">\\(H=X.Y\\)</span>. Déterminer la loi de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(H\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<table>\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"header\">\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(k\\)</span></th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(0\\)</span></th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(1\\)</span></th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(2\\)</span></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"odd\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\prob(H=k)\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{59}{84}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{15}{84}\\)</span></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{10}{84}\\)</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\E (X.Y)\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\E(X+Y)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\E(XY)=0\\times \\frac{59}{84}+1\\times\\frac{15}{84}+2\\times \\frac{10}{84}=\\frac{5}{12}\\)</span><br />\n</p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\E(X+Y)=\\E(X)+\\E(Y)=\\frac{5}{3}+\\frac{1}{3}=2\\)</span></p>\n"
    }
  ]
}